des: This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by FRIESLAND Brands B.V. This skill is used to ask FAQs from a Frico chat bot about itself and Frico products. You can ask things like: "What is your name?", "What is Gouda?", or "Where is the product from?".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
